description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Lake Suwa in Shinano Province
-Kajikazawa in Kai Province
-Ushibori in Hitachi Province
-Umezawa in Sagami province
-Michima Pass in Kai Province
-Asakusa Honganji Temple in Edo
-In the Mountains of Totomi
-Snowy Morning at Koishikawa
-Shimo-Meguro
-Yoshida on the Tokaido
name: Masterpieces of World  - Ukiyo-e, Hokusai's Thirty-Six Views of Mt.Fuji Vol.2-
